data.title: Chubbsafes
data.meta_description: Provides a high degree of protection against burglary and fire. Designed for the financial and commercial sectors' requirements for a high-risk protection
data.text:
Home & Residential

Protect your private valuables with certified safes, fireproof safes, home safes in different levels of certifications.

Bank

Strong rooms and vault doors, as well as certified safes and cabinets to optimise storage, transfer and deposit of cash and documents.

High-Risk Sites

Strong rooms, vault doors, storage cabinets and other solutions to ensure a physical protection of business valuables.

Certified safes

Keep your most important documents and valuables impervious to theft and destruction: Chubbsafes' certified safes are tested and certified to meet the most stringent international standards in security.

Retail safes

Chubbsafes retail safes offer burglary and fire protection in different levels. They are especially designed using improved materials of high density and strength for the protection of cash, important documents and other valuables.

Deposit Safes

Keep banknotes and cash deposits away from prying eyes and potential thieves: Chubbsafes' deposit safes protect your assets while optimising your cash-handling processes.

Fireproof Safes

Ensure your vital paper documents, valuables and data media remain unscathed, even when subjected to high temperatures: Chubbsafes’ fireproof safes are your best defence against the ravages of fire.

Filing Cabinets

Efficiently store your sensitive documents while ensuring your peace of mind: Chubbsafes' fireproof filing cabinets give you the combined benefit of efficient storage and fire resistance in one product.

Home Safes

Ensure your important belongings are protected even when you are not at home: Chubbsafes' home safes are a valuable deterrent to theft and fire.

Security Cabinets

Enhance the security of your bulkiest valuables: Chubbsafes' storage cabinets bring you the best burglary protection and in fire, efficiency and ease of use while optimising your storage space.

Vault Doors

The Chubbsafes' range of vault doors offers certified protection against attacks from a variety of sources: crowbars, high-powered disc cutters and oxyacetylene torches, explosives, diamond-core drill bits and more.

Safe Deposit Boxes

Safe deposit boxes with manual or electronical locking options, offering a high protection for valuables. Installed throughout the globe in many of the world's finest financial institutions

Security Standards

Learn about the security standards that are fulfilled by Chubbsafes products to ensure they not only meet your security expectations, but also respective insurance ratings.

Test Procedures

Learn about the different, extreme security test procedures which Chubbsafes products undergo certifying them for a certain level of burglary or fire resistance.

Certification Institutes

Get to know the independent certification bodies that ensure that the testing and certification processes for Chubbsafes products are carried out correctly.

Manufacturing Certifications

Learn how we list sustainability very highly on our agenda, setting high standards for our products, our employee working conditions and for the environment in which we live.

T2 Certification

Learn how the standard for certifying safes and cabinets providing high burglary resistance has been updated to include advanced tools.

Customer Support

Send a request to Chubbsafes customer support if you need help or have questions about any Chubbsafes product.

Downloads

Conveniently search per product model and find all downloadable content that is related to it.

Glossary

Find a collection of frequently used technical terms and what they mean.

FAQ

Find a collection of frequently asked questions and the answers to those.

Blog

Find interesting insights around how to best secure your valuables and the respective Chubbsafes solutions.

Contact Us

You are interested in our Chubbsafes products? Contact us by filling out a form with your request and we answer you as fast as we can.
